数据源：
<datasource jta="true" jndi-name="java:/ds/test" pool-name="test" enabled="true" use-ccm="true">
    <connection-url>jdbc:derby://localhost:1527/test</connection-url>
    <driver-class>org.apache.derby.jdbc.ClientDriver</driver-class>
    <driver>derbyclient-10.12.1.1.jar</driver>
    <security>
        <user-name>zhyi</user-name>
        <password>zhyi</password>
    </security>
</datasource>

登录模块：
<security-domain name="seedqr" cache-type="default">
    <authentication>
        <login-module code="Database" flag="required">
            <module-option name="dsJndiName" value="java:/ds/test"/>
            <module-option name="principalsQuery" value="select password from users where uname=?"/>
            <module-option name="rolesQuery" value="select urole, 'Roles' from users where uname=?"/>
        </login-module>
    </authentication>
</security-domain>
注意表列必须是 varchar 类型。
